snippet.title: Circus Electrique - Gameplay Overview Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Circus Electrique - Gameplay Overview Trailer

Watch the new Gameplay Overview Trailer and get an in-depth look at how to utilize the right abilities, tactics, positioning and much more. Circus Electrique is a story-driven RPG that's part ⚔️ tactics and part 🎪 circus management with a 🎩 steampunk twist!

Coming 2022
